      .item-description
        h3 Font Flipper
        p Like most graphic designers, I adore typography. I made this site one weekend so I could see all the little details in the fonts on my computer and compare different fonts side-by-side. It was amazing which fonts I ended up falling more in love with, and which ones I realized where not actually that great up close.
