      .item-description
        h3 Nick Malburg: Word Murder
        p Nick Malburg is solo folk/punk musician from Pittsburgh, PA who not only writes catchy tunes, but amazing lyrics as well. The entire album was recorded and mixed by Nick himself in his apartment, so I definately wanted to give his name a handwritten look. He also explained the album's theme was about balancing his thoughts and words with music, which ultimately led to the reflecting top and bottom images.
        a(href="http://nickmalburg.bandcamp.com/", title="Nick Malburg bandcamp page") nickmalburg.bandcamp.com
