      .item-description
        h3 Designly
        p Designly was my first startup failure. I was originally hired to make logos, but the company pivoted into an online store selling site templates built with Twitter Bootstrap and aimed at fellow startups. In addition to designing and coding the site, I created half of the themes offered and a series of coupon cards to be handed out at events.
        a(href="http://designly.herokuapp.com/") designly.herokuapp.com
