      .item-description
        h3 Laura Stevenson & the Cans
        p A few years ago, I started making logos for bands I really enjoy as a way of practicing my design/Illustrator skills. If I can find contact info for the bands, I'll usually send them my "fan art". This particular band liked theirs so much, they made it into a T-shirt. One band member even emailed me a few months later to say it was the most popular shirt they had, was completely sold out, and they are planning to make a second printing with new colors.
        a(href="http://www.laurastevenson.net/home", title="laura stevenson website") laurastevenson.net
