      .item-description
        h3 Freelance League
        p “It would be awesome if we had a cool illustration of superheroes for this landing page”, said my boss one day. I was busy writing some code, but on my lunch break I started doodling some simple heroes. Before I had even finished, he walked past and said, “Well that was easy. This is exactly what I wanted!” He then gave me permission to put the code on hold so I could trace and color them to put on the site.
